the U.S. has concentrated all its efforts to prevent all Muslim
states from getting closer to one another and finally undermine
the coming OIC summit.
</P>
<P>
He accused the U.S. of trying to dominate all oil wells in the
region through its divisive policies.
</P>
<P>
Nouri also voiced Iran's readiness to expand cooperation with
Yemen in various fields, including in parliamentary affairs.
</P>
<P>
The Yemeni minister said that the OIC summit should be
considered as a turning point in making coordination among Islamic
states, adding that Yemen would actively take part in it and hope
other Islamic states to do the same.
</P>
<P>
