areas of economy and commerce and invited Nouri to pay an
official visit to Sanaa.
</P>
<P>
During his meeting with Al-Dafei, Iranian President Mohammad
Khatami said "We are in need of security and tranquility in the
region, based on which we can make up for our past stagnation and
achieve progress, development and greatness in the region."
</P>
<P>
Noting that Iran-Yemen relation was on an upward swing, he
said that the political resolve of the officials of the two
countries would help further expand the bilateral ties. 
