<HEADLINE> U.S. Secretary of State Arrives in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, November 18 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Secretary of State
Madeleine Albright arrived here this evening on a two-day visit to
India, Press Trust of India said.
</P>
<P>
The secretary of state is expected to hold talks with Indian
leaders including Prime Minister Inder Kumar Gujral tomorrow.
</P>
<P>
Albright flew in here from Islamabad. 
</P>
