Australian dollars, ANZ bank edged down two cents to 10.278
Australian dollars ahead of its full year profit results tomorrow,
Westpac closed unchanged at 9.00 Australian dollars, and CBA
closed 26.6 cents down at 16.90 Australian dollars.
</P>
