dollars in the wake of its announcement yesterday of a 39.7
percent increase in interim net profit to 44.8 million US dollars.
</P>
<P>
National turnover hit 605.34 million, worth 1.19 billion US
dollars. Falls outpaced rises 581 to 447 while 418 were steady.
</P>
<P>
Gold was down 60 US cents at 303 US dollars an ounce while the
index lost 10.3 points to close at 950.7.  
