<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, November 18 (Xinhua) -- Kamuzu Banda,the ailing
former president of Malawi, arrived in South Africa Monday for
emergency medical treatment, local newspaper the Star reported
today.
</P>
<P>
