shares, up from Monday's 578.18 million shares.
</P>
<P>
On the Tokyo Foreign Exchange, the U.S. dollar dropped to the
mid-125 yen level.
</P>
<P>
At 5 p.m. local time today, the dollar was quoted at 125.50-53
yen, down from 125.83-88 yen at 9 a.m. in Tokyo and from 125.70-80
yen late Monday in New York. 
