<HEADLINE> OPEC Oil Price Drops Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Vienna, November 17 (Xinhua) -- The average price per barrel of
OPEC's basket of seven crudes dropped slightly to 18.97
U.S. dollars last week, almost the same compared to 18.98 dollars
per barrel a week earlier, statistics released today by the
Vienna-based OPEC Secretariat revealed.
</P>
<P>
The monthly average price in October was 19.54 dollars per
barrel. OPEC strives to reach its benchmark price of 21 dollars
per barrel. 
