<HEADLINE> Brazil's Inflation Continues to Decline </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, November 17 (Xinhua) -- Brazil's inflation rate
during the first 10 months this year reached 3.59 percent, showing
a trend of continued decline from the high of 10 percent last
year.
</P>
